      "span_text": "Following commonly used evaluation in data mining, we also employ k-fold cross validation [CITATION_1] that split the whole golden set of root causes into 10 subsets (i.e., k=10), and repeat the experiments 10 times to calculate the average precision, recall, and F-measure; each time it uses 9 of the subsets as the training data and the other as the testing data."
